1. *Živog* neću da vidim! (I don't want to see *him* alive!)
2. Ovo je *živ* primerak retke vrste ptice. (This is a *live* specimen of a rare bird species.)
3. Našao sam *živog* miša u kuhinji. (I found a *live* mouse in the kitchen.)
4. *Živ* sam, zdrav sam i srećan sam. (I am *alive*, healthy, and happy.)
5. Policija traga za *živim* svedokom nesreće. (The police are searching for a *living* witness of the accident.)
6. Nije dozvoljeno loviti *žive* ribe u ovom jezeru. (It's not allowed to catch *live* fish in this lake.)
7. *Živ* se čovek iznenada pojavio na vratima. (A *living* man suddenly appeared at the door.)
8. Koliko *živ* budeš, toliko ćeš i naučiti. (You will learn as long as you are *alive*.)